<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-56-0830 </DOCNO><TEXT>In the molecular orbital theory of transfer scattering between two heavyions, a simple analytic approximate expression is derived for the exchangepotential which can be applied to the whole region and has definite valuesat R = 0. The simulated spectroscopic factor required now takes morereasonable values than that from BG approximation. The interaction betweenthe two nuclei is discussed and plotted. It depends upon the angularmomentum of both nuclei and the valence particle. Quasimolecular statesmay be formed.</TEXT></DOC>